          <summary>What does each round look like?</summary>
          <b>Round One</b>
          <p>When it's time for round one, we will notify everyone via email to invite you to upload a two minute video to tell us who you are, where you're from, and about the person, cause or organization you would help if you had charitable superpowers.</p>
          
          <p>The Charitable Heroes Founders and Judges will individually review every video submitted. A maximum of 1000 entries will move on to round two.</p>
          <br/>
          <b>Round Two</b>
          <p>This round requires a deep dive into the cause, organization or person you desire to help. When it's time for round two, we will email a link to an online form with ten (10) questions. Our judges will invidividually review all submissions and score individauls. A maximum of 100 entrants will move onto round three.</p>
          <br/>
          <b>Round Three</b>
          <p>The final round will consists of interviews with our judges. Only one winner will be chosen to receive charitable superpowers.</p>
        </details>
      </li>
      
